			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
				In a few focused conversations over about a week, I review your situation through a product, design, and engineering lens — and give you a clear picture of where you are, what's actually going on, and what to do next.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle leading-relaxed">
