				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">2.</span>
					<span><strong class="text-body">Deep-dive meeting</strong>. You get a brief guide beforehand so you come prepared. I learn your project in detail —goals, constraints, what's been tried, what's not working.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">3.</span>
					<span><strong class="text-body">I dig into your materials</strong>. I review what you've provided —wireframes, designs, code, specs— looking for answers to your questions and problems you might not see yet. If I need input from someone on your team, we schedule a short call.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">4.</span>
					<span><strong class="text-body">Findings meeting</strong>. I walk you through what I found and what I recommend. You leave with clear next steps.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
