					<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle leading-relaxed">
						Not at all. Some of the most valuable insights happen at the early idea stage — before any development. If you have a concept but aren't sure it's feasible or how to pursue it, that's a perfect starting point.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg text-body font-normal mb-2">What if I'm already mid-development?</p>
